quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  17,76,"Futhi ngempela bacishe bakusabisa emhlabeni ukuze bakugxoshe kuwona, kepha babengeke bahlale emva kwakho ngaphandle kwesikhashana"
  17,77,(Lena) yindlela yalabo esasibathuma ngaphambilini kwakho abayizithunywa zethu futhi angeke uyithole inguquko endleleni yethu
  17,78,"Yenza umthandazo phakathi nemini kuze kube ubumnyama bobusuku (nokufundwa) kweQur’an (Salatul Fajr) ngokuntwela kokusa, ngempela (ukufundwa) kweQur’an ngokuntwela kokusa kuhlala njalo kufakazelwa izingelosi"
  17,79,Futhi nangezingxenye zobusuku yenza umthandazo kanye nabo njengomthandazo onezeleliwe (uzenzele) wena ukuze iNkosi yakho iyokuvusa kwabafileyo endaweni yokudumisa
  17,80,"Futhi ithi, “Nkosi yami ngingenise ekungeneni okuyiqiniso futhi ungikhiphe ekuphumeni okuyiqiniso futhi ungiphe igunya eliwusizo elivela kuwena”"
  17,81,"Futhi ithi, “iqiniso lafika kwashabalala amanga ngempela amanga ayohlala njalo eshabalala”"
  17,82,Futhi sithumela phansi okwe-Qur’an lokho okwelaphayo kanye nomusa kwabakholwayo futhi ayinezeli lutho kubenzi bokubi ngaphandle kokulahlekelwa
  17,83,Futhi uma sehlisela umusa phezu komuntu uyafulathela futhi aqhelelane nawo futhi uma ethintwa okubi ngasosonke isikhathi uphelelwa ngamandla
  17,84,"Ithi, “Lowo nalowo muntu usebenza ngendlela yakhe ngakho- ke iNkosi yenu yazi kabanzi ngalowo oholwe endleleni (eqondile) ngokwedlulele”"
  17,85,Futhi bayakubuza ngomphefumulo ithi “umphefumulo ungokwempoqo yeNkosi yami futhi anizange ninikezwe lutho ngaphandle kokuncane”
  17,86,Futhi uma sithanda ngempela singakuthatha lokho esakwembula kuwena bese ungabe usazitholela umvikeli obhekene nathi mayelana nako